1
00:00:00,600 --> 00:00:03,967
两星期后 我离开越南
Two weeks later, I left Vietnam.

2
00:00:04,040 --> 00:00:05,528
典礼已经开始
The ceremony was kicked off

3
00:00:05,609 --> 00:00:07,699
首先是总统的演说
with a can did speech by the president

4
00:00:07,779 --> 00:00:12,216
关于扩大越南战争的必要性
regarding the need for further escalation of the war in Vietnam.

5
00:00:12,284 --> 00:00:16,217
约翰逊总统给四名军人颁发了荣誉勋章
Johnson awarded 4 Medals of Honor to men from each of the armed services.

6
00:00:16,291 --> 00:00:18,188
美国深深地感谢你 孩子
America owes you a debt of gratitude, son.

7
00:00:20,131 --> 00:00:22,061
我知道你受过伤
I understand you were wounded.

8
00:00:22,132 --> 00:00:24,062
你的伤口在哪儿？
Where were you hit?

9
00:00:24,137 --> 00:00:25,727
在屁股上 先生
In the but-tocks, sir.

10
00:00:25,805 --> 00:00:27,735
嗯 那一定很好看
Well, that must be a sight.

11
00:00:27,808 --> 00:00:30,569
我倒想瞧一瞧
I'd kinda like to see that.

12
00:00:30,647 --> 00:00:34,411
“我献歌给你 罗宾森太太”
# And here's to you, Mrs. Robinson #

13
00:00:34,486 --> 00:00:37,544
“耶稣对你也特别垂青”
#Jesus loves you more than you will know #

14
00:00:41,195 --> 00:00:44,527
“上帝保佑你 罗宾森太太”
# God bless you, please, Mrs. Robinson #

15
00:00:44,601 --> 00:00:46,258
老天 这孩子！
God damn, son!

